short-description: Clean up your interior by removing the outdated auxiliary cable you plug directly into your smartphone to play music. The Tune2Air WMA3000B works in conjunction with your factory USB/AUX-IN (located in your center console) to allow you to play music in your vehicle via Bluetooth. This device uses A2DP protocol to transmit data at 768kbps, capable of handling very complex audio without any drop in quality. For comparison, the factory Bluetooth handsfree communication only uses a bandwith of 64kbps. Using the Tune2Air creates an entirely new Bluetooth connection to your vehicle - allowing you to retain the functionality of factory handsfree communication while also enabling you to play music via Bluetooth.

cleanDesc: Play2Air Wireless CarPlay Adaptor - BMW & MINI
short-description: The WCP1000 is a plug-and-play wireless CarPlay adapter dongle for iPhones and cars fitted with factory CarPlay systems. Using long, dangling wires to connect your iPhone to CarPlay in order to access your apps and music can be a hassle. Now you can have a wireless connection to your CarPlay that automatically connects your phone without the need for cables. Every time you enter your car, you’re automatically connected to CarPlay. Works for iPhone 5 and up with IOS 9 and above. Use several of your phone’s applications on your CarPlay, such as music, maps, and more. This simple yet handy device will make your CarPlay experience convenient and fun. Features: Automatic Wireless Connection - Wireless CarPlay automatically connects your iPhone without the need for cables. Access your iPhone’s music and applications Fast & Simple Connection - Simply plug the CarPlay adapter into the car’s USB port, go to iPhone’s Bluetooth setup, and connect to Play2Air. Compatible Phones & Vehicles - Wireless Apple CarPlay compatible with iPhone 5 and up with IOS 9 and above. All Vehicles equipped with original factory-fitted wired CarPlay are supported. If you are not sure if you have wired CarPlay, please check with your car dealer for more information. Voice Control - CarPlay wireless supports voice commands to make phone calls, send messages, and activate Siri or to access Google Maps, Waze, Mirrorlink, and iTunes Music. Enjoy ALL Features - Enables you to enjoy all original CarPlay functions wirelessly, including the use of steering wheel buttons to control tracks.

short-description: Aftermarket radio installations are rarely a plug and play operation. They usually require extensive wiring, additional adapters, and a dashboard trim kit. The result is a head unit that sticks out like a sore thumb and doesn't match the design of the interior. Bremmen Parts is aware of these issues and is proud to offer a direct-fit multimedia head unit that alleviates the inherent issues with universal aftermarket radios. Bremmen's Android Multimedia System features an high definition capacitive touch screen and mounts into the same locations as the factory radio. The included wiring harness allows for a nearly plug and play seamless installation. You are able to use your favorite navigation app's by tethering your phones wifi, or use the built in navigation by using a SD card with maps loaded on it. The high resolution touch screen is a upgrade worth its self over cars with factory navigation. Replace screens with dead pixels and up grade the head unit at the same time! Features: 9" 1024x600 capacitive touch screen Cortex A9 Quad Core 1.6GHz 1GB ram Support for MicroSD card and USB flash drive Bluetooth hands-free calling and A2DP audio streaming 4x45W speaker output power Radio tuner with RDS and 54 preset stations. Built-in WiFi modem with support for 802.11b/g/n Supports MirrorLink via USB and WiFi on Android devices and via WiFi on iOS devices. Aftermarket rear view camera support. *Not compatible with factory rear view camera. Supported Digital Media Formats: MP3, MP4, WMA, JPEG Supports Steering Wheel Controls Installation instructions *For vehicles without DSP

cleanDesc: Blaupunkt Bremen SQR 46 DAB 1-DIN Head Unit
short-description: The newly relaunched cult-classic car radio Bremen SQR 46 with many new features! Over the years, some models have become true cult objects, such as the legendary Blaupunkt Bremen SQR 46 from the year 1986. Now we present the reinterpretation of the popular 1-DIN car radio and unite the USPs of the 80s model with new technologies and functions. The result is the Blaupunkt Bremen SQR 46 DAB. The new Bremen SQR 46 DAB has a short installation depth - ideal for classic cars with shortened installation slots. But not only the car radio itself takes the user on a journey through time, the packaging of the device has also been elaborately designed and modeled on the original. Its operating concept, simple design, and crystal clear reception contributed significantly to the popularity of the original Bremen car radio. So we have taken over the styling of the original model in the new edition, but at the same time added a modern Variocolour illumination for the buttons and the display. Thanks to Blaupunkt Codem FM RDS tuner and DAB + digital tuner, the first-class reception remains one of the strengths of the new Youngtimer Car radio. New are the numerous serial interfaces, including two USB ports, an aux port and an SDHC slot - even audio streaming via Bluetooth is not a future piece for the returning legend. The radio carries the "Made for iPhone / iPod" and ensures appropriate compatibility. All settings are permanently saved even when disconnected from the battery. An active DAB + screen antenna is also included. Radio High-End CODEM IV High-End World-Tuner FM (RDS), AM Tuner DAB+ Tuner built-in General Vario Color (for display & button illumination) Fix front panel Permanent memory Short mounting depth IR remote control included in delivery DAB+ onglas antenna included in delivery External BT-microphone included in delivery Data carrier USB, SD, SDHC (up to 32 GB) Media player Audio from USB/SDHC Audio formats MP3, WMA Bluetooth Bluetooth module built-in (HFP, PBAP, A2DP, SPP, AVRCP) Twin-Connect Phonebook access Built-in + external microphone Navigation audio mix Input/Output 1 x front USB 1 x rear USB 1 x front Aux-in Steering wheel control input (programmable) Equalizer/Amplifier 3-band, semi-parametric equalizer Sound presets (Rock, Pop, Classic) X-Bass 4-channel preamp-out (4V) Separate Sub-Out 4 x 50 Watt max. power NOTE: This head unit is an aftermarket solution that may require additional modifications to be made for proper installation. Professional installation recommended.
